finnix-scripts (1.6) unstable; urgency=low

  * Removed all hotplug support
  * Added udev support
  * Made strace boot option less intrusive
  * Removed inittab.uml, UML inittab changes are now handled within finnix-autoconfig
  * Added XenU inittab changes to finnix-autoconfig
  * Commented out network interface down block in finnix-halt (breaks NFS booting in its current state, not really needed anyway)
  * Rewrote rebuildfstab for udev
  * Move rebuildfstab and fstype to /sbin
  * Removed rebuildfstab reference to find
  * Moved rebuildfstab and fstype back to /usr/sbin, too much depends on /usr
  * Added finnix-netboot-server to finnix menu
  * finnix-halt: suppress errors when unmounting /UNIONFS
  * finnix-autoconfig: removed trymount function
  * finnix-autoconfig: rearranged blocks
  * finnix-autoconfig: basic crypt/luks support
  * finnix-autoconfig: basic raid support
  * inittab: replaced rcS with direct finnix-autoconfig
  * rebuildfstab: Added concurrency rescanning
  * finnix-autoconfig: Kill possible error messages on HD mount/swapon -a
  * finnix-autoconfig: Re-enable initial rebuildfstab, then activate udev finnix.rules
  * finnix-autoconfig: Shuffle code blocks, udev is now executed first again
  * finnix-autoconfig: Reordered scanning to raid, lvm, crypt
  * finnix-halt: Test for udev/unionfs
  * finnix-autoconfig: /dev/pts and /dev/shm
  * Marked stable.

